=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過菲林依家嘅優勢主要係dynamic range同埋顏色，而哩啲遲早會俾cmos追上</blockquote>Dynamic 輪左啦，slides 已經好低 連negative film 已經比高階FF爬頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n菲林係贏個色tone因為每隻film有自已既tone, 其他野跟本無所謂，做電影級既特技一早做到同菲林一樣質感，數據黎姐，等如而家個個用到基本既vsco,  將來模擬會更簡單， 我覺得主要係陣味唔同，專業同藝術，鋼琴同電子琴分別，技術都唔同效果唔同，但表達既都一樣"},{"pid":"07e64f0683e7af8870485232da8053f49f55a6a5","tid":508519,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"菲林定位已經變左享受生活態度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n質素？who caresv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />v"},{"pid":"38338d5c447c0a0b5b8546a72ca9b43671869ca8","tid":508519,"uid":44458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:00:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多人用原子筆寫字/做野，都唔代表鉛筆已死既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係autodesk sketchbook同 真筆分別岩d"},{"pid":"e5bb7733907c37228e2a7aa54e29ff9b3aa3c1d5","tid":508519,"uid":18465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:01:18.000Z","msg":"依家好多人玩菲林都唔係志在個畫質"},{"pid":"763a066e38c0100d0f019a40bb2cc5bd1b2c28d7","tid":508519,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07e64f0683e7af8870485232da8053f49f55a6a5","tid":508519,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"菲林定位已經變左享受生活態度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n質素？who caresv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />v"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:02:23.000Z","msg":"玩feel 之嘛，特別係純機械機"},{"pid":"59ad7c7df553a852103456e561f604c38a033667","tid":508519,"uid":44458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:03:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菲林定位已經變左享受生活態度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n質素？who caresv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />v</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以未有vsco之前我已經開po講緊ps模擬菲林研究<br />\n好質素加菲林tone我自已比教喜歡"},{"pid":"2fd0c2a082c0f022afb06681519653f7e59c671e","tid":508519,"uid":38218,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"認同樓主講科技令相機性能大副提升<br />\n相片質素更係無庸置疑<br />\n<br />\n但係換另一個角度睇<br />\n攝影的本質係一種藝術<br />\n當將來的科技去到<br />\n操作極其準確暢順<br />\n相片質素比眼見的還要真實<br />\n我相信有部份影友<br />\n當影到某個位<br />\n會想搵返菲林攝影個種親力親為的感覺<br />\n<br />\n由optical viewfinder 構圖<br />\n到其餘的手動操作<br />\n再到菲林沖曬的過程<br />\n同電子精準操作、以及後期過相入電腦後製相比<br />\n係兩種不同的體驗、得著<br />\n<br />\n我認同菲林攝影的技術未必會再有好大突破<br />\n但係個種精神無咁容易逝去<br />\n而有幾多影友會走入菲林的世界<br />\n相信數量唔會多<br />\n但係個流動依然存在"},{"pid":"9d8d93dd08180093c8fbc34e41d972ebe03bd4e0","tid":508519,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T15:00:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7S1jvNc2DLs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7S1jvNc2DLs&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=651c3df8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7S1jvNc2DLs</a>"},{"pid":"2c44d308086275cb3fd53ff97b2e0b2010c33305","tid":508519,"uid":58791,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"菲林有個特性係cmos or ccd都做唔到既就係立體感，睇過645以上既slide底片先會感覺到<br />\n<br />\n有隻叫做x3既ccd就係模擬菲林既排列方式，影出黎有接近菲林效果，不過而家得sigma用"},{"pid":"c9fe520507042aaf3e4ba0c16a881ecd279b86a7","tid":508519,"uid":4712,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T15:21:56.000Z","msg":"鐘意攝影既<br />\n影菲林係認識佢既歷史 同心態<br />\n下下非黑即白咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6101060d6922c995439076ee4c6c02c8c258ea","tid":508519,"uid":11779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2c44d308086275cb3fd53ff97b2e0b2010c33305","tid":508519,"uid":58791,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"菲林有個特性係cmos or ccd都做唔到既就係立體感，睇過645以上既sl